Benne' biche̱be', dxal-la' gaca chee̱ gaca li ca da naxúaj na lu xiche chee̱ Dios, ca da be̱n Be' Lá'azxa bchálajle̱ne̱' Le̱' gate na' gunná David ca naca chee̱ Judas, benne' guxú'e̱ xel-la waca chee̱ benne' ca' gule̱l-la Jesús lu na' benne' ca'.
