Che ca'an dxenné̱'e̱ lázrdaule le'e ca guca gate na' bdxixruj be'e Dios le'e, gate na' bdxixre̱' le̱'e lawe' lataj, gate na' bdxixre̱' le̱'e lawe' lataj.
